This project contains the source and content of http://blog.roomanna.com.

REQUIREMENTS:
To build, install dependencies:

  Go from golang.org
  Ghostwriter from https://github.com/kurrik/ghostwriter

SERVING CONTENT:

From the blog.roomanna.com directory:

  make watch

The blog will be accessible at http://localhost:9998.  Editing source
files will cause the site to be rebuilt.
